{"type": "article", "id": 19610, "title": "海龟形状的户外灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-24T07:40:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143010pgZSGyx9FPUbrdMq.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏户外灯的灵感源于海龟，灯的主体酷似一个龟壳，上面有近似龟壳花纹的菱形的孔，让灯光从孔隙里透出来，非常轻盈柔和。灯罩的四个脚继续向地面延伸，也模拟了海龟四脚伸出壳外的样子，似乎有自己的生命力。这盏灯的设计来自希腊的建筑师 Konstantinos Kallipolitis，目前还没有生产。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143009PSACHWYb3sGhdILO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143009xqvX0cHU8oM1zN6m.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143010EOlasNxCfX0GA41M.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50470219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}